column5: Me and the mrs,s will be heading to Hamilton Saturday morning. Will be making a stop in at Spiels, to pick up my new treasure.Me and the mrs,s would realy like to do a brunch somewhere in the area and hook up with some members in the area. We should be there by 10 am or so. So Im thinking a 11 am or there abouts for a G2G.But then again,Roy has opened up his tab for me.    Just throwing this out there.  Heck,I might even let you hold my new rod.
Stop by at the Hamilton swap and say hello, me bye.
Googled and done.We,ll be stopping by,me bye.
Only on a sunny day and clear skies
Calling for rain,guess I,ll find it Bruce.LOL
I'll keep a eye out for you Brian, I'll be there. You sellin the new rod? I'll give ya 10 bucks
Bring some coin Brian, I will have lots of deals you cant say no too
Like they say, a Newf can find his way through the dirtiest gale and thickest fog, but on a sunny day.....
